 10:37 u(mei=j oi)/date, to\ geno/menon r(h=ma kaq' o(/lhj th=s i)oudai/aj, a)rca/menoj a)po\ th=j galilai/aj meta\ to\ ba/ptisma o(\ e)kh/rucen I)wa/nnhj,
 10:38 )Ihsou=n to\n a)po\ Nazare/q, w(j e)/xrisen au)to\n o( qeo\j pneu/mati a(gi/w| kai\ duna/mei, o(\j dih=lqen eu)ergetw=n kai\ i)w/menoj pa/ntaj tou\j katadunasteuome/nouj u(po\ tou= diabo/lou, o(/ti o( qeo\j h)=n met' au)tou=.
 10:39 kai\ h(mei=j ma/rturej pa/ntwn w(=n e)poi/hsen e)/n te th=| xw/ra| tw=n )Ioudai/wn kai\ e)n )Ierousalh/m: o(\n kai\ a)nei=lan krema/santej e)pi\ cu/lou.
